tool_define: tool "ask_user" has no `handler` and no `executor`. Either attach a `handler` fn (executor: "harn") or declare an alternate backend, e.g. executor: "host_bridge" + host_capability: "cap.op", executor: "mcp_server" + mcp_server: "server-name", executor: "provider_native". Defining a handlerless tool would surface as `[builtin_call] unhandled: ask_user` at the first model call.
